== Executable GShell WAR ==

Maven plugin that creates an executable WAR that also runs a GShell that can access
JMX Mbeans.

      <plugin>
        <groupId>org.brylex.maven</groupId>
        <artifactId>executable-gshell-war</artifactId>
        <executions>
          <execution>
            <id>doIt</id>
            <phase>package</phase>
            <goals>
              <goal>generate</goal>
            </goals>
          </execution>
        </executions>
        <configuration>
          <applicationName>MyWeb</applicationName>
        </configuration>
      </plugin>

Enjoy!

